<br>
Weapons look pretty good, so I'll just address armor.<br>
<br>
Chest: TW is good, although I recently switched back to using a crafted bp... 3 less AC but the +5 sta +25 hp adds about another 42ish HP for me. I'm not too concerned with STR at the moment myself.<br>
<br>
Legs: Seb scale are fine<br>
Boots: Crafted are fine, I use sebilite tho, they're same ac (12 i think) but the seb have +4 sta<br>
Shoulders: Crafted have nice ac and minor stats, personally I use crested tho, 1 less AC with +6 sta.. you could also go tattered mantle which is 12 ac like crafted but have 20 hp 10 sv disease i think<br>
Bracers: Crafted are good ac, for better stats I'd pick up hero bracer, bracer of scavenging, ice forged shackles.. something along those lines<br>
Arms: Get sebilite scale, same ac as crafted with better stats (4 dex 4 agi and some saves).. or if you're lucky sleeves of the ancients from FM (no drop) have 16 ac and some stats<br>
Gauntlets: Gauntlets of the Black (15 ac 4 str 3 wis) are a nice upgrade... 1 less str but you get 3 ac<br>
Ring: Upgrade to plat or vel<br>
Back: Hard slot.. there's not much in the mid-range that I've seen.. tho if you wanted to just do different you could get a lizardscale and add 5 dex instead of the 10 hp 20 sv cold? Only common upgrades past this would be like an HBC or CoS<br>
Earring: lots of choices here... if you want more AC and stats... go cougar claw, or if you can get em sarnak earrings of station.. I use a diamondine (close to orc fang) and a earring of essence myself (EoE is 30 hp 10 sv magic)<br>
Face: Goblin forged iron mask is high ac like FS, also adds 10 hp... there's prolly some others out there<br>
Neck: I use a Ry`Gorr collar... 9 ac and has 4 sta 4 sv magic, not bad<br>
Head: SSB works<br>
Waist: FBSS is fine<br>
<br>
Just my thoughts... I'm sure there's some higher end stuff available or stuff from velious i haven't seen yet.. but this is what i could think of that would be easily attainable.</font><P><p><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=50985">Eryka</a> &lt;Arma Aquetatis&gt;<br>
